<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='773594' id='t-773594'>standing safely on the pedestrian islands,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='776222' id='t-776222'>and the traffic was flowing,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='778586' id='t-778586'>birds were singing --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='780536' id='t-780536'>(Laughter) --</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='781891' id='t-781891'>the buses were speeding up their dedicated lanes.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='784977' id='t-784977'>It was just fantastic.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:19
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='788675' id='t-788675'>And this is how it looked six years ago.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:22
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='791546' id='t-791546'>And so, I think that the lesson that we have</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='794990' id='t-794990'>from New York is that it's possible</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='798469' id='t-798469'>to change your streets quickly,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='801177' id='t-801177'>it's not expensive, it can provide immediate benefits,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='805171' id='t-805171'>and it can be quite popular.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='807525' id='t-807525'>You just need to reimagine your streets.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='810804' id='t-810804'>They're hidden in plain sight.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:43
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='812869' id='t-812869'>Thank you.</span>
</span>
</p>
